snippet.title: Titanfall 2 - Encore Trailer (2016)
snippet.description:
Official Encore Trailer of Titanfall 2.
Play the highest rated FPS this holiday season with Respawn's Titanfall 2. The encore to the orginal Titanfall has received over 80 scores of 90+ and features no season pass. Call your Titan today and embark on the journey of a lifetime. 

Pre-order Titanfall 2 today and get access to Angel City Map 3 days early: http://x.ea.com/6467

Titanfall 2 is available now for the Xbox One, Playstation 4, and Origin for PC.

“Numb/Encore”
Performed by Linkin Park and Jay-Z
Written by Shawn C. Carter, Kanye Omari West, David Farrell, Brad Delson, Joseph Hahn, Mike Shinoda , Chester Charles Bennington, and Robert G. Bourdon
Published by Universal music – Z songs on behalf of itself and Kenji Kobayashi Music, Nondisclosure Agreement Music, Chesterchaz Publishing, Rob Bourdon Music, Pancakey Cakes Music and Big Bad Mr. Hahn Music
***Jay-Z appears courtesy of Roc-A-Fella Records***
Recording courtesy of Warner Bros. Records
